40:26.853 --> 40:30.734
and it's made to be a sideshow.

40:30.735 --> 40:33.439
And it needs to stop.

40:33.440 --> 40:36.769
Because if this continues
to stay a tourist attraction,

40:36.770 --> 40:40.513
I don't think they're
